{"lemma":"مَلْبَسٌ","slug":"مَلْبَسٌ","root":"ل.ب.س","root_slug":"ل-ب-س","root_link":"/words/roots/ل-ب-س","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n37518"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"garment, dress, suit"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"clothes, clothing","tags":["in-plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root ل ب س (l b s), cf. لَبِسَ (labisa, “to wear”)."},"ipa":["/mal.bas/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37518","headword_ar":"مَلْبَسٌ","root":"lbs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"libaAsN","text_ar":"لِبَاسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA fiY falaAnK malobasN","text_ar":"مَا فِى فَلَانٍ مَلْبَسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no profit"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musotamotaEN","text_ar":"مُسْتَمْتَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in such a one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, [but in the M and A,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA","text_ar":"مَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is omitted, and the only explanation is the word which I have given in Arabic.]) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a fiyhi lamalobasFA","text_ar":"اـِنَّ فِيهِ لَمَلْبَسًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily in him is no pride,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"greatness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"expl. by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA bihi kiborN","text_ar":"مَا بِهِ كِبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kibrN","text_ar":"كِبرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to different authorities [and different copies of the K]: this explanation is by AZ. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoraDa vawobu Almalobasi","text_ar":"اَعْرَضَ ثَوْبُ المَلْبَسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almilobasi","text_ar":"المِلْبَسِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almulobisi","text_ar":"المُلْبِسِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almulotabisi","text_ar":"المُلْتَبِسِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaruDa","text_ar":"عَرُضَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", under which it is explained."}],"source_refs":["IAar","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D9%85%D9%84%D8%A8%D8%B3/","headword_ar":"ملبس","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_1","lexicon_en":"Ibn Manẓūr, Lisān al-ʿArab (d. 1311 CE)","lexicon_ar":"لسان العرب لابن منظور","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=4214#824d37","body_html":"<p>ملبس: المَلَنْبَس: البئر الكثيرة الماء كالقَلَنْبَس والقَلَمَّس؛</p><p>عُكْلِيَّة حكاها كراع.</p>"},{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_8","lexicon_en":"Ibn Sīda al-Mursī, Al-Muḥkam wa-l-Muḥīṭ al-Aʿẓam (d. 1066 CE)","lexicon_ar":"المحكم والمحيط الأعظم لابن سيده الأندلسي","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=4214#c52d14","body_html":"<span class=\"title1\">م ل ب س</span><br><br><span>والمَلَنْبَسُ البِئْرُ الكَثِيرَةُ الماء كالقَلَنْبَسِ والقَلَمَّسِ عُكْلِيّة حكاها كراعٌ</span>"},{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_25","lexicon_en":"Murtaḍa al-Zabīdī, Tāj al-ʿArūs fī Jawāhir al-Qamūs (d. 1790 CE)","lexicon_ar":"تاج العروس لمرتضى الزبيدي","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=4214#25edb4","body_html":"<span class=\"title1\">ملبس</span><br><span>ومِمّا يُسْتَدْرَك عَلَيْهِ: المَلَنْبَسُ، أَهْمَلَه الجَمَاعَةُ، وَقَالَ كُرَاع: هِيَ البِئرُ الكَثِيرَةُ الماءِ، كالقَلَنْبَسِ، والقَلَمَّسِ، عُكْليّةٌ، أَوْرَدَه صاحِبُ اللِّسَان هَكَذَا.</span>"}]}}